Manufacture in which:

- all the materials of [chapter 4](/chapters/04) used must be wholly obtained; 

- any fruit juice (except those of pineapple, lime or grapefruit) of heading No 2009 used must already be originating; 

- the value of any materials of [chapter 17](/chapters/17) used does not exceed **30%** of the ex-works price of the product

Manufacture in which:

- all the materials of [chapter 4](/chapters/04) used must be wholly obtained; 

- any fruit juice (except those of pineapple, lime or grapefruit) of heading No 2009 used must already be originating; 

- the value of any materials of [chapter 17](/chapters/17) used does not exceed **30%** of the ex-works price of the product

Manufacture in which:

- all the materials of [chapter 6](/chapters/06) used must be wholly obtained; 

- the value of all the materials used does not exceed **50%** of the ex-works price of the product

Manufacture in which:

- all the fruit and nuts used must be wholly obtained; 

- the value of any materials of [chapter 17](/chapters/17) used does not exceed **30%** of the value of the ex-works price of the product

Manufacture in which:

- all the materials of [chapter 2](/chapters/02) used must be wholly obtained; 

- all the vegetable materials used must be wholly obtained. However, materials of heading Nos 1507, 1508, 1511 and 1513 may be used

Manufacture in which:

- all the materials of [chapter 2](/chapters/02) and [chapter 4](/chapters/04)  used must be wholly obtained; 

- all the vegetable materials used must be wholly obtained. However, materials of heading Nos 1507, 1508, 1511 and 1513 may be used

Manufacture in which:

- all the materials used are classified within a heading other than that of the product; 

- the value of any materials of [chapter 17](/chapters/17) used does not exceed **30%** of the ex-works price of the product

Manufacture in which:

- all the materials used are classified within a heading other than that of the product; 

- the value of any materials of [chapter 17](/chapters/17) used does not exceed **30%** of the ex-works price of the product

Manufacture in which:

- all the materials used are classified within a heading other than that of the product; 

- the value of any materials of [chapter 17](/chapters/17) used does not exceed **30%** of the ex-works price of the product

Manufacture in which:

- all cereals and derivatives (except durum wheat and its derivatives) used must be wholly obtained; 

- all the materials of [chapter 2](/chapters/02) and [chapter 3](/chapters/03)  used must be wholly obtained

Manufacture in which:

- all the materials used are classified within a heading other than that of the product; 

- the value of any materials of [chapter 17](/chapters/17) used does not exceed **30%** of the ex-works price of the product

